  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Not all that glitters is gold, but this doesn’t matter to a thief: it could still be silver! As greedy as they are skilled, Thieves pursue wealth and cannot resist the temptation to pull some coins out of the pockets of the least careful, whenever the opportunity arises. Whether it is pickpocketing a fishmonger or entering the treasuries of the most supervised buildings on the continent, their sleight of hand and ability to open what should remain closed are unmatched.</span></p>",
